      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Most free AI tools offer genuine free tiers with real functionality. However, they typically have limitations like daily usage caps, watermarks on exports, lower priority during peak times, or restricted features. For light to moderate use, free tiers are often surprisingly capable."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the best free AI image generator?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Leonardo AI offers one of the most generous free tiers with 150 daily tokens, while Ideogram stands out for generating images with accurate text. Stable Diffusion is completely free and open-source if you can run it locally."
      }
