<h2>How to Choose the Right Free AI Tool</h2>
<p><strong>Need a general AI assistant?</strong> ChatGPT's free tier is the most versatile — it handles writing, coding, research, and analysis in one tool. Claude is a strong alternative for longer documents.</p>
<p><strong>Need free AI image generation?</strong> Leonardo AI's 150 daily tokens are the most generous. Ideogram is essential if your images need readable text. Stable Diffusion is best if you want unlimited generations (requires a GPU).</p>
<p><strong>Need free AI coding help?</strong> Cursor gives you a full AI-powered editor for free. v0.dev is perfect for generating React components.</p>
<p><strong>Need free AI video editing?</strong> CapCut offers professional features completely free, though exports include a watermark.</p>
<p><strong>Need free AI voice or music?</strong> ElevenLabs for realistic voiceovers, Suno for original music generation — both have generous free tiers.</p>

<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h3>What is the best free AI tool overall?</h3>
<p>ChatGPT offers the most versatile free AI tool with powerful conversation, writing, coding, and analysis capabilities. For specific tasks, Cursor (coding), Canva (design), and CapCut (video editing) are the best in their categories.</p>

<h3>Are free AI tools really free?</h3>
<p>Most offer genuine free tiers with real functionality. The trade-offs are daily usage caps, watermarks on exports, or slower speeds during peak times. For light to moderate use, free tiers are often surprisingly capable.</p>

<h3>What is the best free AI image generator?</h3>
<p>Leonardo AI offers the most generous free tier with 150 daily tokens. Ideogram excels at generating images with accurate text. Stable Diffusion is completely free and open-source.</p>

<h3>What is the best free AI coding assistant?</h3>
<p>Cursor offers the best free AI coding experience. GitHub Copilot also provides a free tier, and v0.dev is excellent for frontend developers.</p>

<h3>What is the best free AI video editor?</h3>
<p>CapCut is the clear winner with professional-grade AI features completely free. The main limitation is a watermark on exports.</p>

