<h2>How We Test</h2>
<p>Each free AI tool was evaluated on: free tier functionality, usage limits, output quality, ease of use, and overall value. We tested the free tiers extensively — not just the paid versions — to ensure the free experience is genuinely useful. Tools with token/credit limits were tested over multiple days to assess real-world usability. Tools that require credit card information to access the free tier were noted but still included if the free tier offered meaningful value.</p>
